column1: For Mexico all country billing increments are 60/60. For Gambia all country a minimum call duration of 60 seconds and, after the
first minute, billing increments will be per second (billing increment 60/1). For all other destinations billing increments

are in seconds (1/1).
With reference to the  introduction of different MTR based on originating CLI, notified from Italian
mobile Operators Wind – TIM – H3G - Vodafone – Noverca, please be aware that TWT applies surcharges to calls:
•              originating from customers of operators belonging to countries listed in the annexes to our notifications
•              with missing or invalid or modified CLI
•              terminating onto the mobile networks of the mentioned operators
The surcharge will be applied as follows:

•              WIND: 0.0502 Euro/min or 0.0542 USD/min;  only calls from Switzerland mobile Orange, Switzerland mobile Swisscom and calls with missing, invalid or modified CLI 0.1102 Euro/min or 0.1196 USD/min *

•              H3G: AREA A – no surcharge will be applied; AREA B - 0.0200 Euro/min – 0.0225 USD/min *;AREA C – 0.0800 Euro/min - 0.0900 USD/min *;AREA D – 0.1700 Euro/min - 0.1913 USD/min (calls with missing, invalid or modified CLI belongs to this Area)*
* (depending on the currency stated in our agreement – rates in USD can be revised accordingly to exchange rate)
